# VisaClarity AI Rules

Please read the guidelines located at `.ai/skill.md` and `Documentions/AGENT.md` before writing any code or making architectural decisions in this repository.

These documents contain critical rules about:
- TanStack Start & Cloudflare Workers limitations (no Node.js packages)
- Database schema and RLS requirements
- AI Gateway routing
- Design tokens and UI usage
- Project trust and brand guidelines

Do not proceed with significant changes until you have familiarized yourself with these rules.
